long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The CS Go AWP Assimov Live Wallpaper showcases the futuristic and bold aesthetics of the weapon, offering a thrilling visual every time you open a new tab.

CS Go AWP Assimov Live Wallpaper
Google search bar
Addable and removable shortcuts

This Chrome extension delivers a striking chrome wallpaper alongside essential tools for efficient browsing. As one of the top chrome live wallpapers, it adds the intense action of CS
